00:30:19.984 --> 00:30:20.984
- Uau.
- Uau.

00:30:21.653 --> 00:30:23.093
Am scăpat de asta.

00:30:23.988 --> 00:30:25.428
Îl voi lua atunci.

00:30:26.124 --> 00:30:29.103
