- Este blocat.

00:32:37.422 --> 00:32:39.166
- Acum ai distrus...
- Se lipeşte.

00:32:39.190 --> 00:32:40.190
Se lipeste.

00:32:40.425 --> 00:32:42.002
Chiar vei provoca un bruiaj.

00:32:42.026 --> 00:32:43.504
- Emma!
- [râde] Corect.

00:32:43.528 --> 00:32:45.272
Corect.  Cum îl scot acolo?

00:32:45.296 --> 00:32:46.807
Îl împingi în sus.  [râde]

00:32:46.831 --> 00:32:48.409
